name: InkStrokePointer
description: Weak reference to an ink stroke object and its content parent

properties.name: contentId
properties.description: Represents the id of the page content object corresponding to this stroke

properties.name: inkStrokeId
properties.description: Represents the id of the ink stroke

methods.name: load
methods.description: Fills the proxy object created in JavaScript layer with property and object values specified in the parameter.

parameters.name: param
parameters.description: Accepts parameter and relationship names as delimited string or an array. Or, provide [loadOption](loadoption.md) object.
